snippet.title: New York City AMC Reopening; Johnny Depp v Amber Heard; T-1000 Film in the Works; DC Fandome
snippet.description: New York City's AMC Theaters of all theaters of the same chain name is reopening next month; Amber Heard's attorney quits during her lawsuit by Johnny Depp who has accused her of defamation and assault; T-1000 spinoff film to the Terminator films now in development with Ruby Turner and Peyton List cast in the project; Fantasy Springs at Disney Tokyo Sea of Disneyland Tokyo prone to open in 2023; South Park voice actors boycott the upcoming Nosferatu remake; scripts for Alien 6, Predator 2, and Disney's reboot of the Planet of the Apes first-drafted; Ewan McGregor as Jiminy Cricket in LA Pinocchio remake (Disney)? DC Fandome; The Amazing Spider-Man film series; Spider-Man 3 (MCU).
